OL,3,CWomen sue Mitchum deodorant after
OL,4,C'permanent scarring'
OL,6,FWords by Producer Esme Jones
OL,8,FWomen who say they were left with
OL,9,F"permanent scarring" after using
OL,10,FMitchum's roll-on deodorant are
OL,11,Flaunching legal action against the
OL,12,Fcompany.
OL,14,FTikTok users brought the issue to
OL,15,Flight, posting videos showing redness
OL,16,Fand irritation after, they claim,
OL,17,Fusing the brand's 48-hour roll-on anti-
OL,18,Fperspirant and deodorant.
