OL,3,CWomen sue Mitchum deodorant after
OL,4,C'permanent scarring'
OL,6,FOne person described the sensation
OL,7,Flike "volcanoes erupting" out of their
OL,8,Farmpits, while another said it felt
OL,9,Flike it had "burnt through their skin".
OL,11,FMany assumed the issue was caused by a
OL,12,Fchange in the product's formula, but
OL,13,FMitchum UK confirmed that, after an
OL,14,Finvestigation, the problem was linked
OL,15,Fto the brand adopting a different
OL,16,Fmanufacturing process.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
