OL,3,CWomen sue Mitchum deodorant after
OL,4,C'permanent scarring'
OL,6,FThe company apologised and said: "We
OL,7,Fwant to reassure there has been no
OL,8,Fchange to the formula of our products,
OL,9,Fbut we have identified a change in the
OL,10,Fmanufacturing process affecting one of
OL,11,Four raw materials."
OL,13,FA select batch of the roll-on sold in
OL,14,Fthe UK, Ireland and South Africa was
OL,15,Fimpacted by the updated method, and
OL,16,Fthe company has now reverted to the
OL,17,Foriginal process.
OL,19,FBut for many people, it was too late.
