OL,3,CWomen sue Mitchum deodorant after
OL,4,C'permanent scarring'
OL,6,FThey claim the change had caused
OL,7,Fscarring, discolouration, severe
OL,8,Frashes, and in some cases even led to
OL,9,Fhospitalisation.
OL,11,F"It has had a physical and a
OL,12,Fpsychological effect. Some of these
OL,13,Fwomen have not been able to wear their
OL,14,Fnormal clothes because it's showing
OL,15,Fthe scarring or the irritation", said
OL,16,FAnna Malloy from Injury Lawyers 4U who
OL,17,Fis representing the claimants.
