OL,6,F"This product's part of your daily
OL,7,Fhygiene routine. You don't expect it
OL,8,Fto cause you harm or damage. And then
OL,9,Fnow they can't even like shower
OL,10,Fnormally because of the irritation
OL,11,Fwith soap and water and they're
OL,12,Fstruggling to use all the deodorants
OL,13,Fbecause the pain and the irritation".
OL,15,F"You should be able to go out, buy a
OL,16,Fproduct and use it without the risk of
OL,17,Fending up having to seek medical
OL,18,Fattention".
