OL,6,FThe lawsuit will claim Mitchum failed
OL,7,Fto conduct proper safety or quality
OL,8,Fcontrol testing, resulting in what
OL,9,Fthey claim could be life-long
OL,10,Fconsequences for those affected.
OL,12,FA Mitchum UK spokesperson said:
OL,13,F"Mitchum does not comment on pending
OL,14,Flegal matters."
